1
00:00:19,720 --> 00:00:23,250
Gosh! This is bad!

2
00:00:24,070 --> 00:00:25,530
An Chu Xia.

3
00:00:26,570 --> 00:00:28,680
You bully your classmates

4
00:00:28,830 --> 00:00:30,560
and don't respect the teachers.

5
00:00:30,560 --> 00:00:34,070
You have never realized your mistakes.

6
00:00:35,540 --> 00:00:38,790
I always tolerate you and

7
00:00:38,790 --> 00:00:40,970
think you're going to repent.

8
00:00:40,970 --> 00:00:43,670
But you're getting worse.

9
00:00:44,330 --> 00:00:46,070
You deceived me!

10
00:00:47,130 --> 00:00:50,270
Come to my office later.

11
00:00:50,370 --> 00:00:51,810
For the rest,

12
00:00:53,420 --> 00:00:56,410
write a review of 5,000 words.

13
00:00:56,410 --> 00:00:59,890
-5,000 words.
-Impossible.

14
00:00:59,890 --> 00:01:01,250
-In English.
-English? Gosh!

15
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:06,590
The exhibition is over.

16
00:01:07,930 --> 00:01:09,950
Principal, just a minute.

17
00:01:09,950 --> 00:01:14,670
I just knew it. Chu Xia didn't
mean to fight against you.

18
00:01:17,650 --> 00:01:19,230
You Tian.

19
00:01:19,230 --> 00:01:22,230
As a teacher, you should teach
and educate your student.

20
00:01:22,392 --> 00:01:23,570
Yes, I got it.

21
00:01:23,670 --> 00:01:27,670
How can you lead them to break
the school rules to hold an exhibition?

22
00:01:27,670 --> 00:01:28,950
It's my fault.

23
00:01:28,950 --> 00:01:31,050
I feel disappointed.

24
00:01:32,770 --> 00:01:35,350
A fish rots from the head down.

25
00:01:35,350 --> 00:01:39,330
If you set a bad example,
the students will follow your suit.

26
00:01:40,550 --> 00:01:45,580
It had never happened when
Mr. Ma Jian Guo was here.

27
00:01:46,470 --> 00:01:48,370
They used to be disciplined

28
00:01:48,370 --> 00:01:50,420
and well-behaved.

29
00:01:51,050 --> 00:01:52,830
Alright.

30
00:01:52,830 --> 00:01:55,670
I'll guide them after this.
Don't be angry.

31
00:01:55,670 --> 00:01:58,410
Look at you. You are out of your mind.

32
00:02:02,780 --> 00:02:08,450
Honesty and trustworthiness are
the main objective of Stiland College.

33
00:02:08,450 --> 00:02:09,150
Yes.

34
00:02:09,570 --> 00:02:11,450
But you guys

35
00:02:13,030 --> 00:02:15,830
hit classmates, cheat teachers,

36
00:02:15,950 --> 00:02:17,800
act secretly,

37
00:02:18,370 --> 00:02:20,140
bold and reckless.

38
00:02:20,140 --> 00:02:22,890
I can't let it be.

39
00:02:23,340 --> 00:02:28,330
As a principal,
I put a lot of hope on you.

40
00:02:28,390 --> 00:02:31,780
I hope you'll pick yourself up one day.

41
00:02:31,780 --> 00:02:35,530
But you guys make me disappointed.

42
00:02:37,530 --> 00:02:42,120
So, I am going to punish Class B.

43
00:02:42,430 --> 00:02:46,920
Principal, what are you
going to do with us?

44
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:50,350
We would not be
disciplined without rules.

45
00:02:51,130 --> 00:02:56,430
Without improving your
endurance and determination,

46
00:02:56,430 --> 00:02:58,920
you would not do better.

47
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:03,200
I decided to let you all
have a run on the field.

48
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:05,070
-Run?
-Run?

49
00:03:05,070 --> 00:03:08,260
-50 laps for each person.
-50 laps?

50
00:03:08,260 --> 00:03:12,590
Regardless of raining or
thunderstorm, you must finish it.

51
00:03:12,590 --> 00:03:15,960
50 laps! That's it!

52
00:03:18,750 --> 00:03:19,840
Principal.

53
00:03:20,460 --> 00:03:22,210
You can't punish them.

54
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:24,820
Why not?

55
00:03:28,390 --> 00:03:30,090
I've always regretted that

56
00:03:30,830 --> 00:03:33,095
I didn't stand up to protect my student

57
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:35,410
when you punished An Chu Xia
during the gardening.

58
00:03:35,410 --> 00:03:38,610
But today, I can't hide anymore.

59
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:41,530
Don't even run a lap.

60
00:03:41,530 --> 00:03:42,210
You!

61
00:03:42,610 --> 00:03:45,150
You're trying to rebel.

62
00:03:46,530 --> 00:03:48,310
Nothing is wrong with my students.

63
00:03:48,630 --> 00:03:50,600
They shouldn't be punished.

64
00:03:51,410 --> 00:03:52,980
It's my fault.

65
00:03:55,250 --> 00:03:58,476
My students have been
supporting firmly behind me.

66
00:03:58,701 --> 00:04:00,914
But I didn't support them.

67
00:04:02,170 --> 00:04:07,110
Today, I'm going to stand up for them.
They're the best.

68
00:04:07,480 --> 00:04:17,460
-We support Mr. You Tian!
-Support Mr. You Tian!

69
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:20,990
-Support Mr. You Tian!
-Enough!

70
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:34,500
Principal, did you sign the
letter of attorney for Chu Xia?

71
00:04:34,500 --> 00:04:36,460
Yes, I've signed it.

72
00:04:36,670 --> 00:04:38,373
But according to the school rules,

73
00:04:38,398 --> 00:04:40,734
