241
00:18:15,820 --> 00:18:18,390
-Don't argue.
-See you at the auction.

242
00:18:18,390 --> 00:18:21,360
Don't argue. There are
so many paintings here.

243
00:18:21,360 --> 00:18:23,430
Pick if from here.

244
00:18:25,420 --> 00:18:28,080
Look at that. It's nice.

245
00:18:29,750 --> 00:18:34,400
He's young. Will anything happen to him?

246
00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:36,190
Let's get some men to kill him.

247
00:18:43,410 --> 00:18:46,550
They are just joking. Take it easy.

248
00:18:48,950 --> 00:18:50,080
I understand.

249
00:19:33,470 --> 00:19:38,240
Chu Xia!

250
00:19:38,390 --> 00:19:40,710
Did you hear that? Something happened.

251
00:19:40,910 --> 00:19:44,800
Any boy smiled at you?
Or any guy followed behind you?

252
00:19:44,800 --> 00:19:47,590
Don't interrupt.
This is something serious.

253
00:19:47,590 --> 00:19:50,500
Mr. You Tian was fired by the principal.

254
00:19:54,190 --> 00:19:57,860
Don't go to the principal's office.
Mr. You Tian has just left.

255
00:20:00,120 --> 00:20:01,520
Mr. You Tian.

256
00:20:06,940 --> 00:20:07,730
Are you leaving?

257
00:20:13,800 --> 00:20:14,780
What's this?

258
00:20:17,630 --> 00:20:18,240
Keep it.

259
00:20:19,570 --> 00:20:21,710
All my paintings are sold out.

260
00:20:21,870 --> 00:20:23,660
You don't have to compensate me.

261
00:20:25,890 --> 00:20:28,090
You still have one.

262
00:20:28,460 --> 00:20:29,690
I want it.

263
00:20:32,530 --> 00:20:36,620
Although it is valuable for me,

264
00:20:37,080 --> 00:20:38,920
but it doesn't cost that much.

265
00:20:41,130 --> 00:20:45,010
Just keep the balance
as what I pay for the vase for An Chu Xia.

266
00:20:45,850 --> 00:20:46,680
It's okay.

267
00:20:47,280 --> 00:20:50,540
Give me the painting. And you keep this.

268
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:53,960
Okay. I'll keep it then.

269
00:20:58,610 --> 00:20:59,360
Qi Lu.

270
00:21:00,370 --> 00:21:01,430
Thank you.

271
00:21:03,110 --> 00:21:04,390
For what?

272
00:21:05,420 --> 00:21:07,370
I've always been a timid teacher.

273
00:21:07,950 --> 00:21:11,870
I've studied for so long over the years.

274
00:21:12,710 --> 00:21:16,870
Now is the time for me
to go out and practice

275
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:18,890
and see the outside world.

276
00:21:19,820 --> 00:21:22,840
That's good. You found your target.

277
00:21:23,520 --> 00:21:24,600
Congratulations!

278
00:21:26,710 --> 00:21:30,370
Qi Lu, thank you.
And I should thank Chu Xia too.

279
00:21:33,900 --> 00:21:37,950
A man will only start
to appreciate after they lose it.

280
00:21:38,250 --> 00:21:40,370
I treasure everything here.

281
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:48,480
I'm going to look for those
I've ever treasured the most.

282
00:21:48,920 --> 00:21:51,600
Maybe it sounds funny.

283
00:21:51,740 --> 00:21:54,470
But, that's my dream after all.

284
00:21:54,820 --> 00:21:58,480
Qi Lu, you have to treasure
everything in front of you now.

285
00:22:04,220 --> 00:22:04,930
I will.

286
00:22:09,680 --> 00:22:10,420
See you.
